divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: This happened back in the 70 s at night.Saw a bright object high in the sky.Thought it was a star at first,but it was shiny.It moved suddenly from side to side.It zigzaged,forward,& back in the sky.Very fast,and suddenly went up out of sight.I knew,I had seen something strange.
